reviewText: 40 Y-O-V is a must-own movie. I think it's the best there is, and I love watching it over and over again. The cast just plays perfectly off one another and you'll be laughing nearly the entire time. Knocked up, though not as funny as 40 Y-O-V is still really good and worth watching more than once.
Knocked Up, just ok watch one time kind of movie !! 40 Year Old Virgin AWESOME Loved it.........
